   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-b" mid="73" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>The Praying Heart?</FONT><BR><FONT color=#662500>(Why do I keep missing each other on our way?)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-c" mid="74" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel$<BR>It's where the energy of the Monolith is the strongest.<BR>Even Feder and I found it hard to stay there for long.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Meriendel smiles)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-d" mid="75" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel${sound:npc_Marriendel_9437_qu_02.ogg}<BR>That was the first time I saw Feder having a hard time.<BR>He was always so strong no matter what.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-e" mid="76" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Yes, his powers are formidable. </FONT><BR><FONT color=#662500>I've met him a few times in different time periods, but I never managed to fight him.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-f" mid="77" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel$<BR>Fight him? I admire your courage, but I wouldn't recommend that. Even me, who's considered the strongest among all the elves, admire Feder's strength. Well, I'm not sure tentang now though.<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Meriendel smiles confidently)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-g" mid="78" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Are you one of his followers?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-h" mid="79" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel$<BR>More like a... friend maybe?<BR>Feder can't order me around, and I'm sure he doesn't plan on doing that too. But I'll stick with him no matter what.<BR>You know how great he is. I'm happy just to be by his side.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-i" mid="80" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel$<BR>You'll fall for him if you spend some time with him too. He is a human, yet the most powerful creature in this continent. I was always curious how he became so strong.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-j" mid="84" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>His hair?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-j" mid="85" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>His armour?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-j" mid="86" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>His eyes?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel$<BR>And I found the answer!<BR>
<FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, what do you think is the reason that made him so strong?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-k" mid="136" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Huh???</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-k" mid="137" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-k" mid="138" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(It's really hard talking to the people of the past)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel$<BR>Hehe nope! The reason why he's so strong is because he is always Feder himself.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-l" mid="90" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel$<BR>I mean he stayed the same whether he was a poor knight, or the respected king, or a husband of a beautiful princess. He was always Feder. Always.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-m" mid="91" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel$<BR>They say humans change easily, but I found out that Feder is always the same person.<BR>
And I realized that this was what made him so strong... He can control himself from changing.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-n" mid="92" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Hmm... I think I get what you're saying. You mean he has a strong conviction, am I right?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-o" mid="93" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel$<BR>Aha! That would be the best word to describe him. Conviction...<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Meriendel smiles)</FONT><BR>But even with such conviction, Feder... someday he will...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-p" mid="94" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel$<BR>He will die before me. He's a human afterall.<BR>Though I don't want to deny the Goddess's will for the nature of this world, I hope he would live for a long time. He's a good human, and he's leading the other humans well.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-q" mid="95" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Is he really that great...?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-q" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-r" mid="96" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel$<BR>Hmm... I don't know how he is known in your time, but in this world, no one dares to challenge him.<BR>Humans, elves, monsters... everyone praises him for his power and virtue.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1498_meriendel-1-r" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1498_meriendel-1-s" mid="97" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel${sound:npc_Marriendel_9437_qu_03.ogg}<BR>So I hope he doesn't change, and continue to lead the other humans forever if possible....<BR>I believe there are many others who feel the same way as me.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
